<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     OVERVIEW SPLIT
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="sd-overview">
    <div class="sd-section">
        <div class="sd-split">
            <div class="sd-split__img-wrap">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578662996442-48f60103fc96?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=85"
                     alt="Ship side view" />
                <span class="sd-split__img-badge">MV Ocean Sovereign</span>
            </div>
            <div class="sd-split__content">
                <h2>Built for the <span>Open Ocean</span></h2>
                <p>
                    The MV Ocean Sovereign represents the pinnacle of modern bulk carrier design.
                    Constructed at the Hyundai Heavy Industries shipyard in Ulsan, South Korea,
                    she combines cutting-edge naval architecture with decades of operational wisdom.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Her double-hull construction and advanced anti-corrosion coating systems ensure
                    structural integrity across the harshest sea conditions, from the North Atlantic
                    to the Indian Ocean trade corridors.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Equipped with a MAN-B&W two-stroke main engine producing 14,280 kW of shaft power,
                    the vessel achieves a consistent 14.5-knot service speed while maintaining
                    exceptional fuel efficiency ratios well below IMO EEXI thresholds.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     GALLERY
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="sd-gallery-bg">
    <div class="sd-section">
        <div class="sd-section-title">
            <span class="kicker">Visual Tour</span>
            <h2>Ship <span>Gallery</span></h2>
            <p>Explore every angle of the MV Ocean Sovereign — from the bridge to the engine room.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sd-gallery">
            <div class="sd-gallery__item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605745341112-85968b19335b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=85"
